{% endfor %}
Webhook URLs and secrets should match the values in `deploy/.env`.

## 7. Operational limitations

- Replace generated service stubs before serving real traffic.
- Implement backend Bale Mini App HMAC verification before enabling Mini App login.
- Review and apply generated Alembic revisions before production deployment.
- Add TLS termination through your VPS proxy, load balancer, or reverse proxy.
- Add backup, monitoring, log retention, and secret rotation.
- Run real Bale network integration tests before relying on bot behavior.
